DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T180000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T190000
UID:c21c0942165fedd2@sportsbasement.com
DESCRIPTION:Come on out to the Santa Rosa Sports Basement Run Club! This r
 un is all about the fun...lace on up and join us for our weekly run - star
 ting at the store at 9am. It's not just about the miles\; it's about the s
 miles\, the high-fives\, the community vibe\, and sharing our love for Son
 oma County! All levels welcome - hope to see you there! 5k route: https://
 www.strava.com/routes/3283540356429697190
LOCATION:SB Santa Rosa
URL:https://shop.sportsbasement.com/pages/calendar
X-SOURCE:Sports Basement
END:VEVENT
