BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SANTA ROSA RIDE GROUP
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T090000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T110000
UID:6c48f141f9452b6a@sportsbasement.com
DESCRIPTION:Join bike department staffers Cullen and J-Wo for a gorgeous r
 ide through wine country to do some leaf peepin’ as the vineyards change
  color! We are upgrading our normal ride to a more intermittent route\, lo
 nger in distance and a bit more elevation\, including the classic Vine Hil
 l climb. Meet at the store at 9am and be ready to roll out by 9:15am. I he
 ard a rumor there might even be apple cider donuts afterwards… Bring a f
 riend and hope to see you there! *No drop *Helmets required *Need a bike? 
 We rent ‘em! All riders are required to sign our waiver prior to joining
  the ride.
LOCATION:SB Santa Rosa
URL:https://www.strava.com/clubs/552156/group_events/3412607180149289862
X-SOURCE:Sports Basement
END:VEVENT
